            <Title>Sam Ruskovitz</Title>
            <Text>Sam Ruskovitz

		Role in Story:	Initiator of the weirdness in the story.	

		Occupation:	Noir Detective
     	

		Physical Description:	Short and round.  Bowl cut of a hair minus the top.

